Evaluation data for NTCIR-8 Community QA Pilot Task

Aug 2010
----------------------------------------------------

Files
=====
* ntcir8cqa-BA.qrels :
This is the NTCIR-format qrels file (See README.cqa in [2])
based on the Best Answer (BA) selected by the questioner
for each question.
Note that there is exactly one BA per question.
See Section 2.1 in the CQA overview paper part II [1].

* ntcir8cqa-GA.qrels :
This is the NTCIR-format qrels file (See README.cqa in [2])
based on graded assessments of four answer assessors
as described in Section 2.2 (See also Table 2)
in the CQA overview paper part II [1].

* ntcir8cqa-GAW.qrels :
This is the NTCIR-format qrels file (See README.cqa in [2])
based on graded assessments of four answer assessors
as described in Section 4 (See also Table 21)
in the CQA overview paper part II [1].

[1] Sakai et al.:
Overview of the NTCIR-8 Community QA Pilot Task (Part II):
System Evaluation, NTCIR-8 Proceedings, pp.433-457 (2010)
http://research.nii.ac.jp/ntcir/workshop/OnlineProceedings8/
NTCIR/02-NTCIR8-OV-CQA-SakaiT.pdf

[2] NTCIREVAL:
http://research.nii.ac.jp/ntcir/tools/ntcireval-en.html

-----------------------------------------------------
Tetsuya Sakai (Microsoft Research Asia, China)
